      • isValid

        public boolean isValid()
        Determine if object instance has valid attribute data per the server return value Verifies the name is not null and not an empty string. Verifies code is 3 characters in length. Verifies latitude is between +90.0 north pole and -90.0 south pole. Verifies longitude is between +180.0 east prime meridian and -180.0 west prime meridian.
        Returns:
        true if object passes above validation checks
